title: Banana Beanie
body_html:
Halfdays has got your cold-weather accessories covered. This bold yellow beanie will become the piece that you don't leave the house without. 

Free Ground Shipping With Every Order 


Easy Returns. Generate your own return label with Returnly.

 

Cozy Ribbed Knit
To keep you extra warm from the elements
Halfdays Logo
Sewn on the Cuff
Country of Origin
Made in China

Free US Shipping & Returns
We provide free shipping & returns for all US orders. We process your order for shipments Monday - Friday. Once it is processed we’ll pack and ship your order and you will receive a notification with shipping information!
We Ship To Canada!
All orders to Canada will be delivered duty paid (that means no surprise border costs) for an additional shipping fee of $15. International customers are responsible for the cost of return shipping.
When will it arrive?
All domestic orders are sent by ground shipment from Denver, CO and have an approximate shipping time of 3-5 days. 
What is your return policy?
All items with original tags that have not been worn, washed, or altered can be returned for a full refund to the original method of payment within 30 days of receiving your order. International customers are responsible for the cost of return shipping. 
How do I make a return? 
Please use the following link to make a return. If you are returning an international order or need assistance with a return or exchange, please contact us at returns@halfdays.com. We'll get back to you during regular business hours (Monday-Friday from 10:00AM and 5:00 PM Mountain Time).

title: GROOVE face oil
body_html:
The Details:

Groove all day (and night). Good for dry skin or for those who love an ultra-dewy look & feel.

Ingredients: Argan oil, apricot kernel oil, raspberry seed oil. 

Directions: Apply 3-5 drops after moisturizing to complete your skincare routine. Allow 1-3 minutes to absorb prior to applying SPF or makeup. 

Insider Tip: Inspired by Studio 54, apply a drop to your cheekbones post-makeup for a gorgeous glow reminiscent of your favorite highlighter. 

 

What's Inside:

Frolik face oils are 100% pure, vegan, all-natural, and made of sustainably-sourced ingredients.

Free From: Sulfates, parabens, mineral oils, silicones and synthetic fragrances. We never test on animals.

title: RISE face oil
body_html:
The Details:

Rise to all occasions. Good for oily & combo skin types to seal in moisture.

Ingredients: Grapeseed oil, rosehip seed oil. 

Directions: Apply 3-5 drops after moisturizing to complete your skincare routine. Allow 1-3 minutes to absorb prior to applying spf or makeup. Insider

Tip: Apply just before bed as a part of your nighttime routine for a more even complexion come morning.

 

What's Inside:

Frolik face oils are 100% pure, vegan, all-natural, and made of sustainably-sourced ingredients.

Free From: Sulfates, parabens, mineral oils, silicones and synthetic fragrances. We never test on animals.

title: THE PAIR face oil set
body_html:
Can't decide between our two oils? Shop our pair featuring both RISE and GROOVE face oils.

RISE

Good for oily & combo skin types to seal in moisture.

Ingredients: Grapeseed oil, rosehip seed oil. 

Directions: Apply 3-5 drops after moisturizing to complete your skincare routine. Allow 1-3 minutes to absorb prior to applying SPF or makeup. Insider Tip: Apply just before bed as a part of your nighttime routine for a more even complexion come morning.


GROOVE

Good for dry skin or for those who love an ultra-dewy look & feel.

Ingredients: Argan oil, apricot kernel oil, raspberry seed oil. 

Directions: Apply 3-5 drops after moisturizing to complete your skincare routine. Allow 1-3 minutes to absorb prior to applying SPF or makeup. Insider Tip: Apply a drop to your cheekbones post-makeup for a gorgeous glow reminiscent of your favorite highlighter. 

 

What's Inside:

Both GROOVE and RISE face oils are 100% pure, vegan, all-natural, and made of sustainably-sourced ingredients.

Free From: Sulfates, parabens, mineral oils, silicones and synthetic fragrances. We never test on animals.
